snippet.title: Six Sides Of Obscurity (Trailer 2)
snippet.description:
Six sides of obscurity is a story-based RPG that you can play solo or with a team of up to 4 players. You will have endless build possibilities. Creating a character, increasing passive and active abilities according to class, producing equipment, adding tactical bonuses and runes, etc.

Six Sides Of Obscurity now on Steam
